[0.000, "o", "WorkforceGraph\r\n  Intent : Monitor AWS costs, open Jira P1 on breach, escalate to ops\r\n  Roles  : 3\r\n  Source : rule (confidence 46%)\r\n\r\n  в”ңв”Җ cost_monitor  (monitoring)  SLA: max 120s, max $0.05  risk=Risk.LOW\r\n     Monitor cloud/API spend and flag anomalies against a threshold\r\n     вҶ’ hands off to: anomaly_detector, human_escalator\r\n  в”ңв”Җ ticket_creator  (execution)  SLA: max 30s, max $0.05  [idempotent]  risk=Risk.MEDIUM\r\n     Create tickets in Jira, ServiceNow, Linear, or GitHub Issues\r\n     вҶ’ hands off to: notification_sender\r\n  в””в”Җ human_escalator  (governance)  SLA: max 1800s  risk=Risk.HIGH\r\n     Escalate decisions to a human via Slack, email, or CLI approval\r\n"]
